data.description: This home sits on a level lot and has great views and a quite atmosphere.  The great room, and family room gives lots of space for entertaining.  Enjoy the morning sunrise on the back porch or the sunset on the front porch. New Anderson Windows installed this year. New tile on the kitchen floor. Interior was recently painted.   Come enjoy country living!
